::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor stops when he recieves Necro Enari's transmission.

"I believe that Black Arachnia is the leadership," he replies, forgetting to 
activate his comm-link. Realizing his mistake, the bug taps his comm, 
repeating his last sentence.
